rows.label: tlk46310171_02_msg0001
rows.name:
For some reason I can't forget the sight
of Fan-sama's face as she gazed upon
the tales of Alst's creation...

rows.label: tlk46310171_02_msg0002
rows.name:
She looked so strangely melancholy...
I can't imagine what must have been
going through her mind.
